    <item>
      <title>Useful Resources</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/useful-resources/</link>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Jul 2023 16:56:37 -0700</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/useful-resources/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;This page is a just a miscellaneous collection of resources that I&amp;rsquo;ve found useful over the years.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;br/&gt;&#xA;&lt;h1 id=&#34;free-software&#34;&gt;&lt;p style=&#34;text-align:center&#34;&gt;Free software:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;inkscape&#34;&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://inkscape.org&#34;&gt;Inkscape&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;A high-quality vector graphics program&amp;mdash;makes a good, free replacement for Adobe Illustrator.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;blender&#34;&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://blender.org&#34;&gt;Blender&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;This is probably my favorite piece of software&amp;mdash;a highly versatile 3D modeling program. The learning curve is steep, but it&amp;rsquo;s worth it.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;musescore&#34;&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://musescore.org&#34;&gt;MuseScore&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;MuseScore is a simple and straightforward program for creating music scores.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;freecad&#34;&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://freecad.org&#34;&gt;FreeCAD&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;3D computer-assisted design program. Choose this if you&amp;rsquo;re designing something that you&amp;rsquo;re going to physically build, choose Blender for most other 3D modeling.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
